entries.name: Actively Absorbing
entries.description: Any movement toward oncoming contact intended only to protect the recipient of the contact.

entries.name: Ahead
entries.description: One thing (for example, a Skater, a line, the Pack) is “ahead” of another thing, in relation to the track, if it is nearer in the counterclockwise direction than the clockwise direction.

entries.name: Jammer
entries.description: The point scorer for a team.
